---------------- ğŸ Items ------------------

â• Add Items to System
POST /add_items
**Body (JSON):**

{
  "system_id": "movies",
  "items": [
    {"item_id": "123", "title": "Inception"},
    {"item_id": "456", "title": "Interstellar"}
  ]
}


âœï¸ Edit Item in System
PUT /edit_item`
**Body (JSON):**

{
  "system_id": "movies",
  "item_id": "123",
  "updated_fields": {
    "title": "Inception (2010)"
  }
}


