------------------- â­ Ratings ---------------------

â• Add Single Rating
POST /add_rating
**Body (JSON):**

{
  "user_id": "alice123",
  "system": "movies",
  "item_id": "456",
  "value": 4.5
}


âœï¸ Update Single Rating
PUT /update_rating
**Body (JSON):**

{
  "user_id": "alice123",
  "system": "movies",
  "item_id": "456",
  "value": 5.0
}


âŒ Delete Single Rating
DELETE /delete_rating
**Body (JSON):**

{
  "user_id": "alice123",
  "system": "movies",
  "item_id": "456"
}


â• Add Batch Ratings
POST /batch_ratings
**Body (JSON):**

{
  "user_id": "alice123",
  "system": "movies",
  "ratings": [
    {"item_id": "123", "value": 5.0},
    {"item_id": "456", "value": 4.0}
  ]
}


ğŸ“– Get All Ratings of a User in a System
GET /get_ratings_of_user_in_system/<user_id>/<system>

âŒ Delete All Ratings of a User in a System
DELETE /delete_ratings_of_user_in_system/<user_id>/<system>

âŒ Delete All Ratings of a User Across Systems
DELETE /delete_all_user_ratings/<user_id>

âŒ Delete All Ratings in a System
DELETE /delete_all_ratings_in_system/system/<system_id>

ğŸ“– Get Rating for Single Item
GET /rating/<user_id>/<system>/<item_id>


